<div class="title">Aural Cleansing</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca (B. caapi & P. viridis)</div>
<div class="author">by <A HREF="exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=107">Arjuna</A></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Arjuna. "Aural Cleansing: An Experience with Ayahuasca (B. caapi & P. viridis) (exp21836)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 6, 2003. erowid.org/exp/21836</div>

<br/>



